title: Grillo wins in rookie debut at Silverado
text:
> Florida Grillo wins in rookie debut at Silverado Emiliano Grillo, of Argentina, kisses his trophy on the 18th green of the Silverado Resort North Course after winning the Frys.com golf tournament Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Napa, Calif. Grillo won the tournament on the second playoff hole. (AP Photo/Eric Risberg) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
